{"tid":476755,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指採訪佔領期間遭警毆兼扣查 Now工程員入稟向「一哥」索償","createTime":"2017-11-22T09:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T16:39:25.000Z","uid":51904,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed5b868d340b572b96039321b8ddd67b215281c","tid":476755,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"Now TV 新聞台工程人員李小龍於2014年佔領期間，於佔旺區採訪時突然遭警員拉走他手上的鋁梯，並被指用鋁梯襲警，李當時多次表示自己是記者但未被理會，並遭多名警員制服於地上，李因而受傷。李及後遭扣查逾24小時後獲無條件釋放。<br />\n<br />\n李小龍今入稟高院向律政司司長索償，指他當日遭警察毆打受傷。根據司法機構網頁顯示，案件已排期明年5月17日進行提訊。<br />\n<br />\n李事後曾經報案投訴遭警員毆打，但警方沒有起訴任何人，李翌年以個人身份向法院提出私人刑事檢控，向涉事警員追究刑責，但案件未有進展。"},{"pid":"8c81fc9758bc8c1ba1ba0cb37dcb5310e7706530","tid":476755,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"李小龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9428d7632847eeb33ff4b948f8c7d011340918","tid":476755,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:52:39.000Z","msg":"係唔係比人影到果個"},{"pid":"e6b98ed59ff70589e7e9ed8fda02deb86e34ad87","tid":476755,"uid":19287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:58:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xv9bAJFhhmw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxv9bAJFhhmw&d=zHqKsc4XsIYGQJODhmHhQ%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=81398031\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xv9bAJFhhmw</a><br />\n班差佬仲激動過d市民，反而要自己伙記去叫佢地冷靜d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c831efd0fbc932c8e235516f89717ffebcaaafe","tid":476755,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"呢啲黑警同isis有得比，連記者都襲擊"},{"pid":"8c8d684181aeaceaace221b8ff6d4d20d9718bb6","tid":476755,"uid":22696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cb253698209100dd0cb08d